### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000/api/v1
@token = your_token_here

### Health Check
GET http://localhost:8000

### Login
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@correo.com",
  "password": "Admin123!"
}

### Create Task
POST {{baseUrl}}/tasks
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "title": "Nueva tarea de prueba",
  "description": "Esta es una descripci√≥n de prueba",
  "status": "pending"
}

### Get All Tasks (Paginated)
GET {{baseUrl}}/tasks?page=1&page_size=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Tasks Filtered by Status
GET {{baseUrl}}/tasks?page=1&page_size=10&status=pending
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Single Task
GET {{baseUrl}}/tasks/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Update Task
PUT {{baseUrl}}/tasks/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "title": "Tarea actualizada",
  "status": "in_progress"
}

### Update Task - Only Status
PUT {{baseUrl}}/tasks/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "status": "done"
}

### Delete Task
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/tasks/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
